{"TopicId":142728,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"IVA prop placing utility?","CreatedByName":"AlbertoKermov","CreatedById":92461,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T02:55:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"AlbertoKermov","CreatedById":92461,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T02:55:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do mod makers place the props in their IVAs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo far I can only think of modifying the cfg files so that their position/rotation coordinates match the place I want. This is obviously tougher than having an utility to see where they\u0027re being placed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there such a thing? Something like \u0022edit mode\u0022 in Mount and blade.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-29T02:59:15Z\u0022 title=\u002206/29/2016 02:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 29, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by AlbertoKermov\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cxg2827","CreatedById":57380,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T03:01:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222652558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467168958\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002292461\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlbertoKermov\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, AlbertoKermov said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there such a thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes, its done in Unity. Otherwise you have to do it blindly by manually editing the CFG.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou can spawn an existing IVA internal from your KSP directory and then place props, export as a new internal CFG.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPic Below\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022L6IaVpP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022544\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/L6IaVpP.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlbertoKermov","CreatedById":92461,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T04:55:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I\u0027ll look into it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T18:58:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmm... Wonder how difficult it would be for someone to make a plugin for this, similar to what \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/115700-111-nodehelper-tool-used-to-edit-node-positions/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ENodeHelper\u003C/a\u003E does for attachment nodes... ???\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}